    <abstract>
      <p id="P3">RnBeads is a software tool for large-scale analysis and interpretation of DNA methylation data, providing a user-friendly analysis workflow that yields detailed hypertext reports (<ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://rnbeads.mpi-inf.mpg.de">http://rnbeads.mpi-inf.mpg.de</ext-link>). Supported assays include whole genome bisulfite sequencing, reduced representation bisulfite sequencing, Infinium microarrays, and any other protocol that produces high-resolution DNA methylation data. Important applications of RnBeads include the analysis of epigenome-wide association studies and epigenetic biomarker discovery in cancer cohorts.</p>
    </abstract>
